@ValidAnalysisPackageId(message="analysis-package-management.error.analysis-package.id.not-valid-id") @ValidShadowId(message="analysis-package-management.error.analysis-package.id.pattern") @UniqueScriptUuids(message="analysis-package-management.error.analysis-package.scripts.unique-uuids") public class AnalysisPackage extends AbstractShadowableRdcDomainObject implements eu.dzhw.fdz.metadatamanagement.analysispackagemanagement.domain.projection.AnalysisPackageSubDocumentProjection
An analysis package contains all metadata of scripts and analysis data. It will get a DOI (Digital Object Identifier) when the DataAcquisitionProject is released.
